IMPORTANT LOGIC

Availability check must prevent double booking.

Condition:

existing.check_in < new_checkout
AND
existing.check_out > new_checkin

Use this logic in the booking service.

---

STRIPE PAYMENT FLOW

1. frontend calls create-checkout-session
2. backend creates Stripe session
3. redirect to Stripe
4. Stripe webhook confirms payment
5. booking status updated

Never trust frontend payment result.

